Output assets/demo-first-principles.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 580
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 500ms
Type `claude -p --model claude-haiku-4-5-20251001 --plugin-dir .claude-plugin "/first-principles slow release cycle"`
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 28s
